RootCauseAnalysis - INFO -     Result: {'result': 'Based on my analysis, I can see a critical pattern emerging. The cartservice pods (cartservice-0, cartservice-1, cartservice-2) all show only 4 data points each (from 18:11 to 18:14), while other services like shippingservice and redis-cart-0 show complete data throughout the entire fault window (24 data points from 18:11 to 18:34).\n\nThis indicates that the cartservice pods stopped reporting metrics after 18:14, which strongly suggests they crashed or were terminated during the fault window. This is a classic sign of pod crashes leading to cascading failures - when cartservice goes down, it affects frontend services that depend on it, causing high error rates in frontend, and subsequently affecting other dependent services.\n\nThe fact that redis-cart-0 continues to run normally (showing 24 data points with stable pod_processes=1.0) but still shows elevated error_ratio (12.81%) suggests that the errors are coming from the cartservice side not being able to communicate with redis, rather than redis itself having issues.\n\n```json\n{\n  "detected_metric_keys": ["error_ratio", "client_error_ratio", "server_error_ratio", "rrt", "rrt_max", "pod_processes"],\n  "affected_components": ["cartservice-0", "cartservice-1", "cartservice-2"],\n  "metric_summary": "cartservice pods show incomplete metric data (only 4 data points vs expected 24), indicating pod crashes around 18:14. This caused cascading failures with high error ratios in frontend (27-28%), shippingservice (40-49%), and cartservice (18-22%) services.",\n  "time_series_analysis": {\n    "metric_name": "pod_processes",\n    "pattern": "sudden_drop",\n    "critical_timestamps": ["2025-06-05 18:14:00"],\n    "value_change": "1.0 → missing data (pod crash)"\n  },\n  "contradictions": [],\n  "next_verification": {\n    "action": "check_container_restarts",\n    "reason": "cartservice pods appear to have crashed based on missing metric data after 18:14",\n    "suggested_metrics": ["container_restarts"],\n    "suggested_log_keywords": ["OOMKilled", "Error", "exit", "terminated", "panic"]\n  }\n}\n```'}
